  "body_html": "\n  <!-- Meta tag for tracking lecture progress -->\n  <meta id=\"lecture-completion-data\" data-last-lecture-id=\"25245041\" data-last-lecture-url=\"/courses/465756/lectures/25245041\" data-is-completed=\"true\" data-can-access-lecture=\"true\" data-compliance-enabled=\"false\" data-is-open-response-required=\"false\" data-unanswered-open-response-question-ids=\"[]\" data-valid-for-completion=\"true\">\n  <h2 id=\"lecture_heading\" class=\"section-title dsp-flex-xs flex-align-items-center-xs\" data-lecture-id=\"59474001\" data-next-lecture-id=\"23473198\" data-lecture-url=\"/courses/465756/lectures/59474001\" data-next-lecture-url=\"/courses/465756/lectures/23473198\" ,=\"\" data-previous-lecture-url=\"\" data-previous-lecture-id=\"\">\n    <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\">\n        <use xlink:href=\"#icon__Subject\"></use>\n      </svg>\n    &nbsp;\n    ++CHRCH Access\n</h2>\n\n  <!-- Attachment Blocks -->\n<!-- DEBUG: attachments.count=1 -->\n\n  <!-- DEBUG: attachment.id=110136730, kind=text -->\n  <div class=\"lecture-attachment lecture-attachment-type-text\" id=\"lecture-attachment-110136730\">\n    <div class=\"attachment-data\"></div>\n    \n      <div class=\"attachment-data\"></div>\n<div class=\"lecture-text-container\">\n<p></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Join your fellow artists...<br class=\"softbreak\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img data-imageloader=\"\" data-imageloader-src=\"https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/Y7L78F3RnyMjKGmStP3W_NAME_LOGO_BLACK.png\" src=\"https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/Y7L78F3RnyMjKGmStP3W_NAME_LOGO_BLACK.png\" data-imageloader-current-size=\"\" class=\"is-loaded\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">++CHURCH is the official online community for the 'Make Art Not Content' movement. It's where you get to apply everything you've learned in The Mystery School.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Here you will meet all sorts of artists who are on the same path as you.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">But before you enter, I want to warn you…</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">++CHRCH isn’t like other online communities.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">First of all, there’s no “like” button for fake validation. ++CHRCH is about the \"reply\" button. It's about engaging in real conversations with your peers.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Secondly, I DON’T want you to spend time in there every day. ++CHRCH is not Instagram. I want you to be CREATING ART during the week!</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">But on Sundays… That’s when we absolutely want to see your face 😇.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Come in and...</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">1. Post your iterations / Share your art / Get feedback.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">2. Meet your future collaborators.</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">And, of course... Enjoy each week's SUNDAY SERMON (and all the archives)!</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Get your invitation here:</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://makeartnotcontent.com/chrchinvitetms/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">INVITE ME TO ++CHURCH</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong>use the same email as the one you use for The Mystery School or we won't find you</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">(++CHRCH invites go out on Sundays, first-come, first-served ✞)</p><p><br class=\"softbreak\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://makeartnotcontent.com/chrchinvitetms/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-imageloader=\"\" data-imageloader-src=\"https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/iJRPlB0CTrHGdZaLgZT4_church.jpeg\" style=\"\" src=\"https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/iJRPlB0CTrHGdZaLgZT4_church.jpeg\" data-imageloader-current-size=\"\" class=\"is-loaded\"></a></p><p></p>\n</div>\n\n    \n  </div>\n\n\n<!-- Complete and Continue Button -->\n<a class=\"btn complete lecture-complete\" data-cpl-tooltip=\"You must complete all lesson material before progressing.\" data-vpl-tooltip=\"90% of each video must be completed. You have completed %{progress_completed} of the current video.\" href=\"\" role=\"button\" id=\"lecture_content_complete_button\">\n<span class=\"nav-text\">Complete and Continue</span>\n&nbsp;\n<svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"#icon__ArrowForward\"></use>\n  </svg>\n</a>\n\n\n<!-- Comments -->\n<!-- DEBUG: native_comments.count=0 -->\n<!-- DEBUG: total_attachments=1 -->\n\n\n\n<!-- DEBUG: has_disqus=false -->\n\n<div id=\"empty_box\"></div>\n<!-- Scroll to current lecture link position in sidebar -->\n\n"
